---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>明塾 Meijuku｜22期生全員合格の個別指導塾（魚津市）</title>
  <meta name="description" content="魚津市の学習塾 少人数制・個別対応…だから「わかる」「できる」 個別カリキュラム作成で「わかる」 多くの学習機会で「できる」までサポート" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <span class="header__logo">明塾 <small>Meijuku</small></span>
  <nav class="header__nav">
    <a href="#reason">選ばれる理由</a>
    <a href="#course">コース</a>
    <a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a>
  </nav>
  <a href="tel:0765-22-0777" class="header__tel">☎ 0765-22-0777</a>
</header>

<!-- HERO: フルブリード写真＋大型テキストオーバーレイ＋マスコットフローティング -->
<section class="hero">
  <img src={`${base}/images/hero-bg.png`} alt="" class="hero__bg" />
  <div class="hero__tint"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <p class="hero__label">魚津市の学習塾 明塾 Meijuku</p>
    <h1 class="hero__heading">全員合格。</h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">少人数制・個別指導…だから「わかる」「できる」<br />個別カリキュラム作成で「わかる」<br />多くの学習機会で「できる」までサポート</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="#contact" class="hero__cta">無料体験学習に申し込む</a>
      <p class="hero__note">入塾金無料</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <img src={`${base}/images/mascot.png`} alt="" class="hero__mascot" />
</section>

<!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
<section class="philosophy">
  <div class="inner">
    <h2 class="philosophy__heading">ひとりひとりを大切に。</h2>
    <p class="philosophy__text">「目くばり」「気くばり」をモットーに、勉強を通じて「分かる楽しさ」や「知る喜び」そして「忍耐」を知り、それを逆境を乗り切るための「自信」としてもらいたい。</p>
    <p class="philosophy__text">自ら責任指導・継続指導。お子さまの成長を、入塾から卒業まで同じ先生が見届けます。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="wedge"></div>

<!-- REASON -->
<section class="reason" id="reason">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="en">Reason</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h">明塾が選ばれる理由</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="reason__block">
    <div class="reason__img"><img src={`${base}/images/classroom-interior.png`} alt="少人数の教室" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="reason__body inner">
      <span class="reason__num">01</span>
      <h3 class="reason__title">1クラス、最大6人。</h3>
      <p>少人数制だから、ひとりひとりの理解度に合わせて授業の速度も内容も変えます。大人数では埋もれる「わからない」を見逃しません。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="reason__block reason__block--flip">
    <div class="reason__img"><img src={`${base}/images/desk-study.png`} alt="教科書とノート" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="reason__body inner">
      <span class="reason__num">02</span>
      <h3 class="reason__title">塾長が、ずっと見る。</h3>
      <p>学生バイトに任せません。入塾から卒業まで同じ先生が継続指導するから、お子さまの小さな変化も見逃さない。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="reason__block">
    <div class="reason__img"><img src={`${base}/images/stationery.png`} alt="学習用文房具" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="reason__body inner">
      <span class="reason__num">03</span>
      <h3 class="reason__title">追加費用、ゼロ。</h3>
      <p>テスト前の補習も、自主勉の時間も、季節の特別対策も。多くの学習機会で「できる」までサポート。すべて月額の中です。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RESULTS -->
<section class="results">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="results__main">
      <span class="results__number">22</span>
      <span class="results__unit">期生</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="results__statement">高校入試、全員合格。</h2>
    <p class="results__note">富山東・魚津・新川をはじめ、県内外の志望校へ。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COURSE -->
<section class="course" id="course">
  <div class="course__layout">
    <div class="course__photo">
      <img src={`${base}/images/desk-study.png`} alt="" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="course__badge">入塾金<strong>無料</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="course__data">
      <p class="en">Course</p>
      <h2 class="sec-h">コースと料金</h2>
      <h3 class="course__label">小学生</h3>
      <div class="course__row"><span>週2回</span><strong>¥12,000<small>/月</small></strong></div>
      <div class="course__row"><span>週3回</span><strong>¥16,800<small>/月</small></strong></div>
      <h3 class="course__label">中学1年</h3>
      <div class="course__row"><span>週2〜3回</span><strong>¥17,500<small>/月</small></strong></div>
      <h3 class="course__label">中学2年</h3>
      <div class="course__row"><span>週2〜3回</span><strong>¥20,000<small>/月</small></strong></div>
      <h3 class="course__label">中学3年</h3>
      <div class="course__row"><span>週2回〜</span><strong>¥20,000〜<small>/月</small></strong></div>
      <p class="course__note">教材費は実費（1冊¥1,000〜1,800）。補習・テスト対策の追加費用なし。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TEACHER -->
<section class="teacher">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="en">Teacher</p>
    <h2 class="teacher__name">明吉 道雄<span class="teacher__role">明塾 塾長</span></h2>
    <blockquote class="teacher__quote">
      勉強を通じて「分かる楽しさ」や「知る喜び」、そして「忍耐」を知ってほしい。<br />
      それが逆境を乗り切るための「自信」になるから。
    </blockquote>
    <p class="teacher__bio">集団指導から個別指導へ。長年の経験を経て明塾を設立。モットーは「目くばり・気くばり」。ひとりひとりの名前と弱点を覚えて、必要な時に必要な声をかける。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="en">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h">よくある質問</h2>
    <div class="faq__item"><p class="faq__q">途中から入塾してもついていけますか？</p><p class="faq__a">個別カリキュラムなので、お子さまの学力に合わせて始められます。月途中は日割り計算です。</p></div>
    <div class="faq__item"><p class="faq__q">部活と両立できますか？</p><p class="faq__a">学校帰りの直接来塾に対応。回数・時間の変更も柔軟にできます。</p></div>
    <div class="faq__item"><p class="faq__q">5教科すべて教えてもらえますか？</p><p class="faq__a">英語・数学・理科・社会・国語の全5教科に対応。苦手は重点的に、得意は先取りで。</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<footer class="cta" id="contact">
  <div class="inner">
    <img src={`${base}/images/mascot.png`} alt="" class="cta__mascot" />
    <h2 class="cta__heading">まずは、無料体験から。</h2>
    <p class="cta__sub">お子さまの「わかる」が始まる場所を、一度のぞいてみてください。</p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a href="tel:0765-22-0777" class="cta__tel"><span class="cta__tel-num">0765-22-0777</span><span class="cta__tel-note">午後3時〜10時</span></a>
      <a href="mailto:meijuku.uozu@gmail.com" class="cta__mail">メールで問い合わせる</a>
    </div>
    <address class="cta__addr">〒937-0046 富山県魚津市中央通り2丁目3-21</address>
    <p class="cta__copy">© 明塾 Meijuku</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<div class="sticky"><a href="#contact" class="sticky__btn">無料体験に申し込む</a></div>

</body>
</html>

<style>
:root {
  --azuki: #745a6a;
  --azuki-dark: #6e5364;
  --bg: #e5e3db;
  --bg-light: #edebe5;
  --white: #fff;
  --text: #3a3a3a;
  --text-soft: #5a5a5a;
  --text-muted: #8a8a8a;
  --rule: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --serif: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  --sans: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
}

*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: var(--sans); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.9; letter-spacing: 0.04em; overflow-x: hidden; background: var(--bg); padding-bottom: 70px; }
img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
.inner { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; }
.en { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--azuki); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; opacity: 0.6; }
.sec-h { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3.5vw, 1.7rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 2rem; }

/* HEADER */
.header { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(229,227,219,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
.header__logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text); }
.header__logo small { font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.65em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: 0.2em; }
.header__nav { display: none; }
.header__tel { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--azuki); }
@media (min-width: 769px) { .header__nav { display: flex; gap: 1.8rem; } .header__nav a { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-soft); } }

/* HERO: フルブリード写真＋大型テキスト＋マスコットフローティング */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100svh;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 44px;
}
.hero__bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover; object-position: center 40%;
}
.hero__tint {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    rgba(116,90,106,0.7) 0%,
    rgba(116,90,106,0.35) 40%,
    transparent 70%
  );
}
.hero__content {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  max-width: 680px;
}
.hero__label {
  font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white); opacity: 0.7;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.hero__heading {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 12vw, 7rem);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.hero__sub {
  font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 1.8vw, 0.95rem);
  line-height: 1.9; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.hero__actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero__cta {
  display: inline-block; padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  background: var(--white); color: var(--azuki);
  font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.88rem;
  transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
}
.hero__cta:hover { background: var(--bg); }
.hero__note { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 700; }
.hero__mascot {
  position: absolute;
  right: 5%; bottom: 8%;
  width: clamp(100px, 15vw, 180px);
  z-index: 3;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15));
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero__tint {
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(116,90,106,0.75) 0%,
      rgba(116,90,106,0.4) 50%,
      rgba(116,90,106,0.15) 100%
    );
  }
  .hero__mascot { right: 3%; bottom: 3%; width: 90px; }
}

/* PHILOSOPHY */
.philosophy { padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 0; background: var(--white); text-align: center; }
.philosophy__heading { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3.5vw, 1.8rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--azuki); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.philosophy__text { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 2; }

/* WEDGE */
.wedge { height: 40px; background: var(--bg); clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 50% 100%); }

/* REASON */
.reason { padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem) 0 0; background: var(--bg); }
.reason__block { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; margin-bottom: 2px; background: var(--white); }
.reason__img { overflow: hidden; height: 220px; }
.reason__img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
.reason__body { padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem; }
.reason__num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--azuki); opacity: 0.12; line-height: 1; }
.reason__title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0.3rem 0 0.7rem; line-height: 1.4; }
.reason__body p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 1.9; }
@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .reason__block { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; min-height: 340px; }
  .reason__block--flip .reason__img { order: 2; }
  .reason__block--flip .reason__body { order: 1; }
  .reason__img { height: auto; }
  .reason__body { padding: 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
}

/* RESULTS */
.results { padding: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0; background: var(--azuki); color: var(--white); text-align: center; }
.results__main { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: center; gap: 0.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.results__number { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(5rem, 16vw, 10rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; color: var(--bg); }
.results__unit { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem); font-weight: 700; }
.results__statement { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.results__note { font-size: 0.82rem; opacity: 0.5; }

/* COURSE */
.course { background: var(--white); }
.course__layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.course__photo { position: relative; overflow: hidden; height: 180px; }
.course__photo img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
.course__badge { position: absolute; bottom: 1rem; left: 1rem; z-index: 2; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--white); background: var(--azuki); padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem; line-height: 1.3; }
.course__badge strong { font-size: 1.8rem; display: block; }
.course__data { padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem) 1.5rem; }
.course__label { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 1rem 0 0.2rem; }
.course__label:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
.course__row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 0.4rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-size: 0.9rem; }
.course__row strong { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text); }
.course__row small { font-size: 0.6em; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; }
.course__note { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .course__layout { grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr; }
  .course__photo { height: auto; min-height: 420px; }
  .course__data { padding: 2.5rem; }
}

/* TEACHER */
.teacher { padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem) 0; background: var(--bg); }
.teacher__name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text); margin-top: 0.3rem; }
.teacher__role { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: 0.8rem; }
.teacher__quote { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 2.1; color: var(--text); padding: 1.2rem 0; margin: 1rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-style: normal; border-left: none; }
.teacher__bio { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 1.9; }

/* FAQ */
.faq { padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem) 0; background: var(--white); }
.faq__item { padding: 1.1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.faq__q { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.faq__q::before { content: 'Q. '; color: var(--azuki); }
.faq__a { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; }
.faq__a::before { content: 'A.'; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }

/* CTA */
.cta { padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem) 0 2rem; background: var(--azuki); color: var(--white); text-align: center; font-style: normal; }
.cta__mascot { width: 100px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; }
.cta__heading { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3.5vw, 1.6rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.cta__sub { font-size: 0.88rem; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.cta__actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.8rem; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.cta__tel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); transition: background 0.3s; }
.cta__tel:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
.cta__tel-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
.cta__tel-note { font-size: 0.68rem; opacity: 0.6; }
.cta__mail { display: inline-block; padding: 0.7rem 1.8rem; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: background 0.3s; }
.cta__mail:hover { background: var(--bg-light); }
.cta__addr { font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.45; font-style: normal; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.cta__copy { font-size: 0.65rem; opacity: 0.2; }

/* STICKY */
.sticky { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 90; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: rgba(229,227,219,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.sticky__btn { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--azuki); color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; }
@media (min-width: 769px) { .sticky { display: none; } }
</style>
